typeProperties.script:
source(output(
		{Scored Label Mean} as double,
		{Scored Label Standard Deviation} as double
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false) ~> source1
source1 select(mapColumn(
		{Scored Label Mean},
		{Scored Label Standard Deviation}
	)) ~> Select1
Select1 sink(input(
		Scored_Label_Mean as decimal(20,2),
		Scored_Label_Standard_Deviation as decimal(20,2)
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	format: 'table',
	deletable:false,
	insertable:true,
	updateable:false,
	upsertable:false) ~> sink1
